test run
set enable_simd
set regalloc_checker
target s390x

function %sshr_i16x8(i16x8, i32) -> i16x8 {
block0(v0: i16x8, v1: i32):
    v2 = sshr v0, v1
    return v2
}
; note: because of the shifted-in sign-bit, lane 0 remains -1 == 0xffff, whereas lane 4 has been shifted to -8 == 0xfff8
